{"tid":1524584,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［蘋果/立場請即入］警察831記者會必問-極重要","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T05:52:34.000Z","uid":288312,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ebbb1477ba6b2f54becc66f2473790195f91ffa2","tid":1524584,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:35:50.000Z","msg":"831晚四圍都有狗扮前線<br />\n好快狗一定開記者會强烈譴責<br />\n當然就算俾晒片佢地都一定<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死口唔認</span></span>係自己放汽油彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我建議記者問任何野之前都要加以下呢句：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n「阿sir/madam, 唔係事必要你講, 但如果你所講嘅並非事實, 你可能已經觸犯左公職人員行為失當罪, 你所講嘅亦會成為罪證。」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢句野係真係有法律效力(曾蔭權之前入罪就係因為喺電台訪問講錯野), 加上pprb條友一聽到果下嘅反應, 自然會令大家知道真正嘅答案!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請幫推及廣傳!!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55ed0362de57c0312fc35795e2036e1808ed7f0c","tid":1524584,"uid":95487,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:37:34.000Z","msg":"其實係入場開記招前<br />\n記者一齊問會唔會好d"},{"pid":"1cfefc3d1d539cfd8020d4cc04a